room_title: Escape room "The Asylum" by Grand Forks Escape Room in Grand Forks
room_address: 2500 S Columbia Rd, Grand Forks, ND 58201
room_description: You've been falsely accused of being criminally insane and are committed to the old Brookfield insane asylum. Upon arriving you are placed into the legendary Room 104, whose previous resident managed to escape under mysterious circumstances. You have one hour to follow in his footsteps and escape the asylum before you become a permanent resident.
